es.indarsoft.iso8583core.types

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.indarsoft.iso8583core.types.Field

  • public final class Field
extends Object
    Field class that maps a filed data entry in /config/*.xml file 

     Attributes:
 
    
        id                              field id
        lengthType                      LengthType 
        name                            field name
        fieldFormat                     FieldFormatType 
        fieldLength                     field length
        fieldCodification               FieldCodificationType
 
    
        For Variable Length Data types :
 
    
        lengthFormat                    LengthFormatType
        lengthOfLengthField             length for the length field 
        minfieldLength                  minimum length 
        maxfieldLength                  maximum length
